mount - Attach external data sources

Usage:
  mount                           List current mounts
  mount -t <type> <src> <dest>    Create mount

Mount types:
  http      HTTP/REST endpoint
  webhook   Webhook receiver
  cron      Scheduled tasks

Examples:
  mount
  mount -t http https://api.example.com/data /mnt/external
  mount -t find model_name=users /mnt/active-users

Mounts persist in ~/.config/mounts.json
